# GKError.Code.gameUnrecognized

**Case**

The system can’t complete the requested operation because Game Center doesn’t recognize the app.

## Declaration

```swift
case gameUnrecognized
```

## Discussion

Ensure the app’s `bundleID` is correct.

## Configuration Errors

- **GKError.Code.notSupported**: The app doesn’t have Game Center enabled.
- **GKError.Code.appUnlisted**: The system can’t complete the requested operation because the game isn’t available on the App Store.
